Uses of Class
checkersMain.CheckersPlayerInterface.CheckersPlayerEvent

Packages that use CheckersPlayerInterface.CheckersPlayerEvent
checkersMain Provides the main classes and interfaces needed to simulate a Checkers game. 
checkersPlayer Provides several implementations of the CheckersPlayerInterface. 
 

Uses of CheckersPlayerInterface.CheckersPlayerEvent in checkersMain
 

Methods in checkersMain with parameters of type CheckersPlayerInterface.CheckersPlayerEvent
 int CheckersPlayerInterface.choosePlyIndex(CheckersPlayerInterface.CheckersPlayerEvent cpe)
          Returns the ply index of this CheckersPlayerInterface's choice that corresponds to the CheckersBoard and CheckersBoard.Ply returned from the methods CheckersBoard.getSuccessor(int) or CheckersBoard.getPly(int) respectively.
 void CheckersPlayerInterface.gameEnded(CheckersPlayerInterface.CheckersPlayerEvent cpe)
          Notifies the CheckersPlayerInterface that the checkers game has ended.
 void CheckersPlayerInterface.gameStarted(CheckersPlayerInterface.CheckersPlayerEvent cpe)
          Notifies CheckersPlayerInterface that it is beginning a new game.
 void CheckersPlayerInterface.remainingTimeChanged(CheckersPlayerInterface.CheckersPlayerEvent cpe)
          Notifies this CheckersPlayerInterface on how much time is remaining for its CheckersPlayerInterface.choosePlyIndex(CheckersPlayerEvent) method to run.
